# ========================================
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# ========================================

# 1. Add these variables in Vercel Dashboard:
#    Project → Settings → Environment Variables

# 2. For each variable:
#    - Click "Add"
#    - Enter Name (e.g., PHONEPE_MERCHANT_ID)
#    - Enter Value
#    - Select Environments: Production, Preview, Development

# 3. After adding PhonePe URLs:
#    - Replace YOUR_VERCEL_URL with actual URL
#    - Example: https://sneha-saurabha-2025-26.vercel.app

# 4. After adding all variables:
#    - Click "Redeploy" to apply changes

# 5. Security:
#    - Never commit .env files to Git
#    - Keep credentials secret
#    - Change admin password immediately after first login

# ========================================
# PHONEPE APPROVAL PROCESS
# ========================================

# After deployment:
# 1. Submit these URLs to PhonePe merchant dashboard
# 2. PhonePe will verify your live website
# 3. After approval, update credentials:
#    - PHONEPE_MERCHANT_ID → Your production merchant ID
#    - PHONEPE_SALT_KEY → Your production salt key
#    - PHONEPE_API_URL → https://api.phonepe.com/apis/hermes
# 4. Redeploy to apply production credentials

